                    <div id="page-content">
                        

<p>此处存放了所有曾被挂上首页的中国分部原创主题作品。</p>
<hr />
<p>1. <strong>图书馆</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/wanderers:little-red-riding-hood">小红帽</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhi-zi-jiu-jun" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4326424); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4326424&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="zhi_zi-jiu_jun" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4326424)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/zhi-zi-jiu-jun" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4326424); return false;">zhi_zi-jiu_jun</a></span></li>
<li><em>小红帽常常会忘记自己是一只狼。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>2. <strong>农历新年</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/happy-new-year-my-love">新年快乐！</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/austinyzhao" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3968381); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3968381&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="AustinYZhao" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3968381)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/austinyzhao" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3968381); return false;">AustinYZhao</a></span></li>
<li><em>不论发生何事，过新年一事总不会落下。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>3. <em>從缺</em></p>
<p>4. <strong>春天</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/simple-things-spring">平凡的故事：春</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drsee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2928788); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2928788&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="DrSee" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2928788)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/drsee" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2928788); return false;">DrSee</a></span></li>
<li><em>只是一些发生在春天的往事而已。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>5. <strong>劳动</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/i-manager-wang">我，王经理</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ashausesall" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1546989); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1546989&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="ashausesall" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1546989)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/ashausesall" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1546989); return false;">ashausesall</a></span></li>
<li><em>你们几个，不要玩了，滚回去工作！</em></li>
</ul>
<p>6. <strong>广告</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/wanderers:xiang-cheng-kai-fa-piao">香城开发票，兼代办证、代购产品、代写论文</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4055881&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="Etinjat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4055881)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/etinjat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4055881); return false;">Etinjat</a></span></li>
<li><em>先验证、后付款,欢迎您咨询!</em></li>
</ul>
<p>7. <strong>审核</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/doom">末日</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/archibald1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2265704); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2265704&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="Archibald1" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2265704)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/archibald1" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2265704); return false;">Archibald1</a></span></li>
<li><em>Ding成功拯救了基金会&#8230;&#8230;虽然是以最丢人的方式达成的。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>8. <strong>神話</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/wanderers:lexicon-noricst">诺莱斯志异</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4457426&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="Enflowerz" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4457426)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/enflowerz" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4457426); return false;">Enflowerz</a></span></li>
<li><em>这里记述着一个已化为灰烬的文明的一切。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>9. <strong>建国</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/foundation-of-the-empire">立國之本</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mscarlet" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1745583); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=1745583&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="MScarlet" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=1745583)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/mscarlet" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(1745583); return false;">MScarlet</a></span></li>
<li><em>国家的建立一般都伴随着一个个可歌可泣的故事；但这个国家的建立，卻是从一件玩具开始的。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>10. <strong>逆模因</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/antimeme-guide">简单易懂的逆模因识别指南（节选）</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3662783&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="TimeElapsed" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3662783)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/timeelapsed" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3662783); return false;">TimeElapsed</a></span></li>
<li><em>相信我，你不会想，也不会知道作者的下场是怎样的。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>11. <strong>超形上学</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/veleafer-s-proposal">SCP-CN-001：Veleafer的提案-演绎部</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veleafer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2934041); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2934041&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="Veleafer" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2934041)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/veleafer" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2934041); return false;">Veleafer</a></span></li>
<li><em>将会有一场RK级叙事崩毁，我们的作者，某个更上叙事的人把我们的叙事线打了一个结，想看好戏。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>12. <strong>圣诞节</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/merry-freakmas">圣诞快乐</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/forgotmydrug" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4313927); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4313927&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="ForgotMyDrug" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4313927)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/forgotmydrug" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4313927); return false;">ForgotMyDrug</a></span></li>
<li><em>在圣诞节的夜里，小乔治渡过了一個难忘的晚上。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>13. <strong>新年</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/new-year-bell">新年钟声 暨 Dr.Marleak是怎样收容跨年晚会的</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simon-arran" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4354147); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=4354147&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="Simon Arran" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=4354147)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/simon-arran" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(4354147); return false;">Simon Arran</a></span></li>
<li><em>随着Duang的一声，基金会又平安踏进新的一年，Ramen。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>14. <strong>科幻</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/kill-the-world">K-96时停对策雷</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bitchangelover" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2995593); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=2995593&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="bitchangelover" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=2995593)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/bitchangelover" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(2995593); return false;">bitchangelover</a></span></li>
<li><em>要对付世上最难缠的时停能力持有者，你需要简单管用的理论、将理论化为现实的手段、以及必要的牺牲。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>15. <strong>因果</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/scp-cn-1485">SCP-CN-1485</a></strong> - 将尔晦明，彼凭一叩 by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=5480202&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="sciencekiller" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=5480202)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/sciencekiller" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(5480202); return false;">sciencekiller</a></span></li>
<li><em>记住，别像我们一样带入外来物。</em></li>
</ul>
<p>16. <strong>Bright博士</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/jack-bright-resting-at-last">Jack Bright在此安息</a></strong> by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3935168&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="Lyrics Linn" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3935168)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/lyrics-linn" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3935168); return false;">Lyrics Linn</a></span></li>
<li><em>每说一声再见，就是死去一点。——《漫长的告别》</em></li>
</ul>
<p>17. <strong>北欧神话</strong></p>
<ul>
<li><strong><a href="/scp-cn-1143">SCP-CN-1143</a></strong> - 北欧的终结 by <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3396110&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1607601038" alt="Kcorena" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3396110)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/kcorena" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3396110); return false;">Kcorena</a></span></li>
<li><em>“只要那孩子还立在大地上，他就是不败的”</em></li>
</ul>
<p>18. <strong>赛博朋克</strong></p>
